WEBVTT

00:02.113 --> 00:05.361
???????

00:05.897 --> 00:09.437
<i>a series of questions we answer
through the choices we make.</i>

00:13.577 --> 00:15.727
<i>Sometimes they work against us.</i>

00:17.000 --> 00:23.074
Advertise your product or brand here
